**LIX Calculator:** https://www.readabilityformulas.com/lix-formula.php

**Formula:** LIX = (Number of words / Number of sentences) + (Number of long words / Number of words) * 100

**Number of words:** 59
**Number of sentences:** 5
**Number of long words:** 11 (words with more than 6 letters)

**Calculation:**

* (59 / 5) + (11 / 59) * 100 = 11.83 + 18.64 = 30.47

**Result:** LIX=30.47